Benedictum --- Tres Fata (Three Fates)

The three sisters of fate — Clotho, Lachesis, Atropos — each cast a number.
None may question them. None may appeal.

Clotho spins the thread. She reveals her number.

fatum lux nox

Lachesis measures the thread. She reveals her number.

fatum lux nox

Atropos cuts the thread. She reveals her number. The last word.

fatum lux nox
